name: Barbarian
description: One little guy isn't enough to do much, but placing roughly 150289 of them can bring chaos to even the strongest and most well-defended base. All for zero cost! Splendid.

name: Pink Slime
description: Pink Slimes would be really scary if they were 10x bigger, covered in spikes, and had a bloodthirsty intent to kill. Luckily, they don't, and are pretty and little, so our everyday lives continue in peace.

name: Mute
description: What are you doing MAX?!? Arya exclaims as little Maxingz teamkills him for the 3rd time in a row. Maybe this outcome is unavoidable.

name: Loot Bug
description: Pesky little thing that does nothing but drops lots of shiny rock when popped. Unfortunately you can't pop it now for extra wishes.

name: Gunboat
description: The weakest little boat in the gosh darn ocean. Well it's trying its best, and every shot counts.

name: ME Terminal
description: Me when I play normal vanilla minecraft and I have to mine blocks one by one and WHERE IS ME TERMINAL AUUUGH. Me when I play modded minecraft: ME Terminal

name: Workday Website
description: Your life is nothing! You serve zero purpose! You should kill yourself now! And give somebody else a piece of that oxygen and ozone layer, that's covered up so we can breathe inside this blue trapped bubble. Because what are you here for? To worship me? Kill yourself. I mean that, with a hundred percent. With a thousand percent.

name: Galvanized Square Steel
description: Does not come with eco-friendly wood veneers, nor screws borrowed from my aunt.

name: Elder Lemurian
description: A wise man once said, give an Elder Lemurian a fish, and he will be fed for a day. But teach an Elder Lemurian how to fish, and he will be fed for the rest of his life.

name: Soraka
description: This is fine.

name: Benjamin
description: Executing hack! Executing hack! Executing hack! I am hungry for vengeance! Someones not popping bloons! Executing hack! Executing

name: Soyjack (Default)
description: The wojak is a curious creature forced into existence by the pressures of evolution. Its remarkable similarities to human beings, not only in stature, but also circumstance, have it cemented as a top-priority research subject for teenage men all around the world

name: El Primo
description: Bro these teammates can't be real man. Like how does this kevx guy did 0 damage. He must have been twiddling his thumbs and kicking his feet distracted by something

name: Berilia
description: I'm supposed to write some flavour text here, but I've never played Barotrauma. The industrial revolution and its consequences have been a disaster for the human race.

name: Bloodhound
description: When life gives you lemons, you have to Allfather guides all -- my parents, Boone... To taka responsibility for all is to taka the power of the gods. I am no god. And I am not nothing...

name: Industrial District
description: Guys, I just started the game and I am already $3000 in debt. How do you guys even make money? Should I dedicate... more industrial zoning?

name: Bracken
description: Don't you just want to give this guy a hug?

name: Quartz Deposit
description: Bro, how are all of these nodes impure bruh. I just want a normal, regular, quartz node so we can start making an actually good factory out of it.

name: SFU Fire Alarm
description: Imagine being a young, aspiring, university student, dreaming of a life of adventure and determination, but then you are faced with the reality that you won't be getting any sleep. Ever. Because of this thing.

name: Average Food Served at Orchard Commons Kitchen
description: Imagine being a young, aspiring, university student, dreaming of a life of adventure and determination, but then you are faced with the reality that you won't be eating any good food. For the foreseeable future. Because of this place.

name: Ayanokoji
description: Steps to be awesome at manipulating: 1 maintain average of 50% in courses. 2 be sure to not show your emotions. Then you can manipulate people into doing what you want. Pretty epic.

name: Lillia
description: WHAT did my midlaner just say ?!??!?!?!??

name: Lagtrain
description: 2GBps Train, Paket pheonix, high-speed ethernet, wired into my brain, coursing through my veins, I'll break through the monotony of my life, and take the lag out of this train.

name: Patrick Bateman
description: 2am wake up. 2:30am do 5000 pushups. 3:00am commit tax fraud. 4am edging. 5am shower, shit, brush teeth, get ready for breakfast. 6am get out of bed, and seize the day. Sigmamale schedule

name: Minato Aqua
description: If Minato Aqua has 1000 fans, I am one of them. If Minato Aqua has 100 fans, I am one of them. If Minato Aqua has 10 fans, I am one of them. If Minato Aqua has 1 fan, I am that fan. If Minato Aqua has no fans, that means I am no more.
